            <lg xml:id="TK148">
<l>piṟaṉmaṉai nōkkāta pērāṇmai cāṉṟōrk</l>
<l>kaṟaṉoṉṟō vāṉṟa voḻukku</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>For the noble, the great manhood that has no regard for the "house" of another</l>
<l>is not only their duty, but their noble conduct.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
